Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:06.36,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,In a few minutes, the opening ceremony of the Daihaseisai will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:11.33,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, at Academy City, a lot of parents and siblings of our students are present.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid lunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone like one of Academy City's famous maid lunches?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid lunches from the Ryouran Domestic Studies Institute for Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:24.71,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, lunches made by a maid-apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:29.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, there sure are a lot of different schools in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:35.72,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's because they consolidated all the educational institutions of the world in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.14,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.62,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault, please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:43.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you happen to know where Tokiwadai Middle School is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:47.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:49.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokiwadai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:50.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokiwadai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:52.81,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:55.49,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not open to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.25,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.71,0:00:59.69,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, where is that Mikoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:03.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this Mikoto-san your younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:07.83,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Touya-san. Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:10.02,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.01,Index II main overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.01,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... what do you mean by "again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Isn't that Touma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:15.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:19.64,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose to you then I'll do a penalty game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:21.93,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.30,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:25.32,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything means anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:28.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, you'll also face the penalty if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:34.07,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do anything you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:35.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:41.07,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all the self-confidence you have after running your mouth like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:43.83,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:46.72,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to cry your way out later!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.08,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikoto-chan is energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:28.22,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to start the Daihaseisai, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need to greet them at the opening ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:35.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I can go out in front of people in this form?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.94,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let us get on with our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:42.11,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it regarding the magicians that snuck into Academy City?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking advantage of the relaxed security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.12,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Our reports have confirmed two intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:53.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A high ranking Roman Catholic, and a courier in her employ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:58.02,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They aim to trade a certain object.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain object?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.16,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:08.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the "Stab Sword".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that it's able to slay a dragon and stitch it to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:18.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's successfully delivered, we, Anglican Church, will be in deep trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So it serves as a tactical weapon of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:30.45,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest problem is that the transaction for this Stab Sword will take place inside Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:37.24,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to use that boy as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, Touma. I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just eat breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:51.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there are so many attractive smells everywhere, I can't stand it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.35,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's food culture is the pinnacle of culinary temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:00.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go get some later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:01.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Later?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.07,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:04.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first match is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:07.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,All the events I'll be participating in are marked on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.45,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:15.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma is so very dry today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.84,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:27.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does everyone look so exhausted before we've even started?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:35.12,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fighting over the tactics we were going to use against other schools, and used up what little energy we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.64,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that putting the cart before the horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A match between students is like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.53,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this lethargy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:53.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, Kamijou! Did your laziness infect everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I only just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:59.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it means everyone lost their drive because you came late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You reached here after me, Fukiyose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had administration work to do, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:11.64,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou-san has gotten stuck in an unfortunate reality, and he can't stand up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.49,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just mild anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, use this sports drink to fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:22.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate those who use misfortune or bad luck as an excuse to lead a sloppily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you look lethargic, everyone else will lose their motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you need to get your act together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.72,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.49,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.67,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's worried about the Wrench Stick match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.69,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:07:00.20,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit that our facilities and curriculum are inadequate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not the fault of the students!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:08.09,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it due to their poor performance that the Board of Directors won't provide more funding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Managing so many failures must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.61,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's no success or failure for students!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.37,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They each just have their own personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite optimistic of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wrench Stick match is about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:28.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return this debt by destroying those failures of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.33,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't failures, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.23,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.32,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have no motivation to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.75,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The first match is the Wrench Stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The two teams are entering now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could beat our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't have got a heatstroke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.30,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.84,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Short-Hair doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.27,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna cheer for Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:25.24,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I cheer for that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.86,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to see which school would win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.03,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's obvious that mine will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:34.36,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What should do when I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he'll do whatever I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.50,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that determination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.46,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that they're serious about winning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.78,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I be forced to do if he wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:17.20,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did everyone try so hard to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:22.15,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you won, seeing everyone injured like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.24,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei is... Sensei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.25,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.21,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:09.71,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I came here to get my cellphone to call someone I've lost track of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.30,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any bad intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.77,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.09,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.62,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The battery is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.71,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me something to eat, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the stands, there'll be mountains of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.12,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.22,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.54,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a parade coming through here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get across the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:59.17,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can cross it using an underground street three km to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:00.15,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three km?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's so close that I can almost touch it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.34,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to endure until the end of the Ball Rolling match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.35,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.07,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:22.30,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, I've got my winning selection!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:31.12,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,First place in the Borrowing Race is Misaka Mikoto from Tokiwadai Middle School!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.64,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Borrowing Race?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:35.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.39,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to find a high school student who had participated in the first event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You satisfied the requirements, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:46.35,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There should have been a bunch of others who--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.27,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, here, drink this--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it can't be helped, I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.32,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:17.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought about us working hard in this hot sun while Shirai-san rested alone in an air conditioned room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:24.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to get you out here to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thank you for this perfect friendship appropriately later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have any problems arisen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:37.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,In first place, we have Misaka Mikoto, who's still in good condition after reaching the finish line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.72,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,She continues to show exuberance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:42.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Onee-sama--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:50.28,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of the companion who ran with her really gave a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.93,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we got separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Index be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:32.15,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Academy City is hosting tourists, the security is lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:37.16,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the magicians have decided to use this opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.98,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,We've confirmed the presence of two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.69,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia Lorenzetti of the Roman Catholic Church,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.88,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,and the courier she hired, Oriana Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:47.51,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,A courier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:51.70,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan to conduct a trade of a spiritual weapon that the Church has handed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.80,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they do that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.56,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Academy City the furthest one could get from the occult?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.64,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:05.10,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Academy City's current situation means that neither science nor magic can take action here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:09.50,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the only people who can act are your comrades already in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.05,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about Kanzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:13.36,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she supposed to be a Saint?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.89,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki cannot be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.80,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.00,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the nature of this particular spiritual weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.00,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.70,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, the name of this spiritual weapon is "Stab Sword".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:31.01,Index II main I,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it can kill a Saint with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.16,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.39,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kamijou Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:49.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how the Son of God was killed on the cross, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.20,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was nailed--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:15:00.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stab Sword carries the religious meaning of nailing and stabbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:04.63,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,amplified, concentrated, and focused to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:11.25,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless against normal humans, but if the opponent is a Saint, it can kill with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:16.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these magicians thinking, trading such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:18.32,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's war, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.27,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A Saint is the magical equivalent of a nuclear weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:26.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are lots of magicians who aren't Saints, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.51,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,They can fight even without Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.81,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:35.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about whether or not we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:40.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,A war may break out if they manage to create the illusion of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:47.96,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If the situation is this serious, shouldn't we ask Index for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:49.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.88,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use that forbidden index this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:55.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not allow her to get near the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.18,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,and we can't let her become aware of this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:01.68,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.70,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happened, all sights will be set on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:07.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The magicians on the outside are still looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:14.52,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she makes a move, the magicians who notice will come flooding in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:21.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, this means we have to keep Index away from this situation so the other magicians don't notice her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I rushed over after getting a call from Yomikawa-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.82,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I became worried after finding you looking listless like a shrunken vegetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:38.16,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.67,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But where has Touma gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.98,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,About lunch, you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:49.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:55.99,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been feeling that Touma's going to be separated from me all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.69,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:04.02,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister-chan wants to enjoy the Daihaseisai with Kamijou-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.09,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.20,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an event that Sister-chan can take part in as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:11.50,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.82,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.79,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:24.30,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, you looked like a hero who was about to face the final boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.46,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you look like you're about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.97,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are hungry then, why you don't eat lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:31.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind that, have you seen Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.57,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that Sister, I just saw her down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:37.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:44.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like she was pulled aside by that famous miniature-sized teacher in Kamijou Touma's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.83,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:58.67,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.14,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:07.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad making you change at place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:17.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times will you peep like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.40,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Index-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:33.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:34.87,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident! An accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:36.41,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:44.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here searching for Tsukuyomi-sensei for administrative work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:50.61,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.33,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing--?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.55,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:03.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Can't you put any effort towards making this event a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.27,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,In what event is our school participating now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.17,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:13.04,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like your brain is lacking nutrition, you need to get some sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:17.05,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even with that, Kamijou-san's stupidity won't be cured!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.36,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sad just saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:24.35,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The second-year girls tug-of-war, and the third-year boys triathlon,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,which side do you want to cheer for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.74,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, you want the girls side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.01,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since you're that Kamijou after all--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.13,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, stop pulling my collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.62,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.30,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.16,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kamijou, is the Daihaseisai really that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.85,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been absent-minded,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.83,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,like there's something else on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:56.65,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel that today is boring,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:20:01.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,then it means that I have some shortcomings as an administrative committee member.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:03.93,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:08.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,As one of the people who worked hard to plan all these events,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:12.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that everyone can share some wonderful memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:15.08,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm just being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:23.26,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it, there's just no fixing that mind of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:24.78,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:25.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.16,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me, Kamijou Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.60,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.90,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to such crowded places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:44.42,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.47,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your forehead has turned red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:51.81,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.69,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,As an apology for knocking into you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:57.31,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,would you like a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.44,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I want a kiss--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.95,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be going back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.00,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:22.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.45,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Oriana Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:25.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.10,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say your name out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:30.39,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice can be heard by those around you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.27,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind that, I've already got some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:37.58,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,The spell Onee-san cast on me was just broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.56,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:39.91,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:42.73,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sure gets me all hot and bothered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.36,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying indecent things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:46.82,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any countermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.48,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:52.38,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I have to lose this boy who's following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.92,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oriana toys with us while running around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.12,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl risks his life when searching for the spell she cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.59,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the place we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:35.43,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: "Route Disturb."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:38.80,Index II main,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, the story begins.
